==English==

===Etymology===
From [[w:Japanese language|Japanese]] [[布団]] (ふとん, futon).

===Noun===
'''futon''' (''Plural:'' '''futon''' ''or'' [[futons]])

# A thin [[mattress]] of [[tuft]]ed [[cotton]] or similar [[material]], placed on a [[floor]] or on a raised, [[foldable]] [[frame]] as a [[bed]].

